  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators are conducting a randomized trial of behavioral treatments for young
      children with insomnia. The investigators are comparing the improvement in sleep patterns
      after families are given access to Internet sleep instructions compared to DVD sleep
      instructions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
